<P><PB REF="35">From <HI>Da|uid</HI> Saint <HI>Mathew</HI> reckons the legall line of Christ, to let vs see that christ was law|full
King of the Iewes, &amp; succeeded by the law as neerest of kinne to sit vp|on
the throne of his father <HI>Dauid.</HI></P>
<LIST>
<ITEM>34 David
<LIST>
