<ITEM>Ieconias.</ITEM>
</LIST></ITEM>
</LIST>
<P>Here ends the race of <HI>Salomon.</HI></P>
<P>From <HI>Da|uid</HI>
Saint <HI>Luke</HI> rec|kons
the naturall line of Christ, to let vs see that Christ is the sonne of <HI>Dauid,</HI> naturally discended of him by <HI>Nathan</HI> according to the flesh, for the <HI>Messi|ah</HI>
was promised to be the sonne of <HI>Dauid.</HI></P>
